      <abstract displayLabel="Abstract">The U.S. standards and conformity assessment system is complex and
                involves cooperation between the Government and private sector. This CD-ROM provides
                an overview of the roles and responsibilities of those involved in the U.S. system.
                It addresses standards, conformity assessment and metrology concepts and lays out
                the means by which the U.S. system interfaces with the international community.
                NISTIR 6978 is a website artifact that can be viewed on your preferred internet
                browser.</abstract>
